messages.content: Hi, thank you for calling Vacation Village Resorts. This is Jamie, a virtual agent on a recorded line. How can I help you today?
Pay maintenance fees.
Let me get your maintenance payment link ready. Alright, you want to pay
your maintenance fees. Would you like me
to send you a link to make your payment now?
Yes.
I was able to pull up a record using your phone number. Can you tell me your first and last name
so I can make sure I have the right account?
Cynthia Serum.
I didn’t find a match for Cynthia Serum. Can you please spell your first and last
name for me, just to make sure I have it right?
E m I l.
C I r o n e.
Thanks for spelling that out. Can you tell me
your state of residence?
Florida.
Great, I have you verified. Go ahead and let me know what you need help with
regarding your maintenance fees.
Pay.
I can help you pay your maintenance fees for your property. The email I have
on file is cccirone@msn.com and the phone number is two zero five -- three eight three -- seven two zero two. Are these correct?
Yes.
Got it, working on your payment link now.
Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No.
Alright, you’ll receive a link to pay your maintenance fees shortly
by email and text. Have a great rest of your day.
